f analytic aids in planning  organizing  and controlling in a changing environment are included  Organizational and personal values  ethics  management of change  organizational power  politics  and managerial strategy and tactics are discussed within the context of the military organization  These courses must be taken with appropriate leadership laboratories    Back to Top   Print Friendly Page   All catalogues   2016 Virginia Military Institute  Powered by the Acalog  Academic Catalog Management System   ACMS  Mobile Site 